{"tid":1304761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘗試執一執五大訴求，focus 返大家戰略","createTime":"2019-07-10T16:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T17:32:47.000Z","uid":132376,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"37da9d95f64d9f190e2732e36f41e5a0c74c94f7","tid":1304761,"uid":132376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一，永不追究義士</strong></span></span><br />\n首先對支持開反送中而又所謂堅守法治嘅人講，屌你老母，冇義士嘅話６２０不過係香港民主最黑暗嘅其中一日。至於班開明少少又睇緊連登嘅共產黨，你嘅落台階係：不論係剎停檢控定係特赦，的確唔符合法律程序公義，但寫得出黎就係要用，用在非常特別嘅政治事件。今次係香港政治制度嘅缺憾令大家集體盲咗炒車，迫市民無所不用其極兼且對一國兩制完全失去信心。永不追究抗爭者係為咗保住個垃圾一國兩制，改革政制杜絕類似事件，所以唔會成為案例<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>二，獨立調查惡法責任</strong></span></span><br />\n繼續強調獨立調查委員會係審哂成件事包括埋班官，邊個政黨提監警會就係玩針對，要前腺警受哂，幫班涼冷氣高層孭鑊。呢個建議本身多懶中立人士提，依家見到監警會做野就好似想收貨，唔好比佢沉，推佢出去可能有意想不到嘅政治地震<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>三，２０２０普選立法會</strong></span></span><br />\n難得條bill 寫到咁明，就唔好咁繞口咩真雙普選，時間係２０２０，目標係立法會，目的係杜絕所有惡法，拎咗立法會你鍾意罷免特首都得呀，仲驚乜野提名委員會？之後有咩野餐呀餵動物呀，全部拎２０２０年９月倒數幾多百日黎計，你唔搞政改就直接２０２０年９月自己成立一個立法會出黎，睇下你急定我地急<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>四，撤回兩隻字都唔識讀點樣年年考第一呀</strong></span></span><br />\n我無野講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五，收回暴動指控</strong></span></span><br />\n我要見律師"},{"pid":"3e30686e14e976f988d4406b3a84702fe1a542d1","tid":1304761,"uid":132376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3ceef120e8eac0985884bf2e0a71f7c4b047652a","tid":1304761,"uid":209679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"普選放第一"},{"pid":"2ab5eb343f2dd5f9a0c71a57a25aa5e7e12f0825","tid":1304761,"uid":132376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161e776c81a5fad99c3feb74b323b66e9f83e21f","tid":1304761,"uid":132376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97046d91ecb2892bfc810d3f8d08dccda470336e","tid":1304761,"uid":88675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:02:02.000Z","msg":"推！ ！"},{"pid":"82cc2fb4056102f39bad994e2359c3cf6fba0ac8","tid":1304761,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"永不追究改做特赦所有義士"},{"pid":"09b56ac5d5c86dcac2fff3ed5849276113f53882","tid":1304761,"uid":12197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82cc2fb4056102f39bad994e2359c3cf6fba0ac8","tid":1304761,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"永不追究改做特赦所有義士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"唔係等於話佢地真係有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369a77f46630f06e47c07f5b50ff31a704690a26","tid":1304761,"uid":132376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ceef120e8eac0985884bf2e0a71f7c4b047652a","tid":1304761,"uid":209679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"普選放第一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"明白你 concern, 但係義士呢筆佢地企得最硬, 而且好多反送中嘅人意志唔夠堅定, 和理非口唔講割蓆但心入面超想, 李柱銘篇文我真心有D 驚好多人同佢一樣諗法"},{"pid":"53ca6028a0e4c3b3afbb3d850f460f0713dfdd12","tid":1304761,"uid":269732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09844fe492d3f5b1b18790990e807607d1388b7b","tid":1304761,"uid":269732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57334354835cba724a2c5b1803315806a762f592","ti